    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Others have already answered this, but here is a way of finding it without jumping into menus.</p>\n<p>Try hitting <code>⌘ + Shift + A</code> on Mac or <code>CTRL + SHIFT + A</code> on Linux and type the <code>Show parameter name hints</code> into the search bar.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/Qm8PP.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/Qm8PP.png\" alt=\"Show parameter appears when searching from the Action/Option name search bar\" /></a></p>\n"
