    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<ol>\n<li><code>⌘ + Shift + A</code></li>\n<li>Type <code>Inlay Hints</code></li>\n<li><strong>Make sure that the language of your choice has <code>Types</code> set up properly!!!</strong> Here's an example for Kotlin:\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5ZixZ.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5ZixZ.png\" alt=\"Inlay Hints settings\" /></a></li>\n</ol>\n"
