    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>As of 2022, it's been renamed to &quot;inlay hints&quot;</p>\n<p>You can disable it by pressing <code>shift</code> + <code>shift</code>, then type <code>inlay hints</code> and then disable it.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/uySEj.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/uySEj.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
